ol.li:
If the word is a compound one, and you want to keep it on the same line, then wrap it in
				an inline element with the outputclass attribute set. From the CSS change
				its styles to  white-space:nowrap;.
				Example:.. <ph outputclass="no-hyphenation">T-shirt</ph>...*[outpuctlass ~= "no-hyphenation"] {
	white-space: nowrap;
}
